{"tid":859293,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"日本留學","createTime":"2018-10-12T11:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T13:54:46.000Z","uid":140503,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"957a2f7577d340f2d944c5c08ab621a74a3a6e1a","tid":859293,"uid":140503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"有沒人10月到日本東京留學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎左差唔多成個禮拜都沒咩野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學校教緊嘅野暫時都仲應付到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係沒野好做啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想識下d同學仔都好難 個個一放學就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個室友又難得理我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知點樣先可以識到新朋友啊<br />\n利申 死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19eb92fd8d32209dc2509f7206f113224dca271d","tid":859293,"uid":140503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"連登唔係好多崇日撚嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad5573da7cdf44e205aeafae4e4a183f7d6a5e89","tid":859293,"uid":140503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"橙 毒撚開po沒人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d8aaa0609ea179ce768fa2932ee2f2a00fd7bc","tid":859293,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a6f1a9f93a81827856b5ca1f9486c373abdea0c","tid":859293,"uid":140503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13d8aaa0609ea179ce768fa2932ee2f2a00fd7bc","tid":859293,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T12: